Javier Hernandez scored the only goal of the two legs in the Champions League quarter-final second leg at the Bernabeu . 
  Arda Turan was sent off for Atletico Madrid in the 76th minute after a foul on Sergio Ramos . 
  Cristiano Ronaldo scored the opening goal of both legs for Real Madrid . 
  The result means Real Madrid will face Barcelona in the semi-finals . 
 